"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Quick Start with Rust\\n\\nThis guide will walk you through the steps to set up and start using the dYdX API Rust library.\\n\\n::::steps\\n\\n## Install Rust and Cargo\\n\\nChoose and install [Rust](https://www.rust-lang.org/tools/install) and [Cargo](https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/getting-started/installation.html) for your system.\\n\\n## Clone the dydx client repo\\n\\n```bash\\ngit clone https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients.git\\n```\\n\\n## Run an example\\n\\nGo to the Rust client library.\\n\\n```bash\\ncd v4-clients/v4-client-rs\\n```\\n\\nNow, we can run an example file. Let's run `accounts_endpoint` example.\\n\\n```bash\\ncargo run --example account_endpoint\\n```\\n\\n::::\\n\\n**Now, you can play around with all the available examples. Happy trading!**\\n\\n\\n:::tip[Rust Crate]\\nThe Rust client is also available through the crates.io [crate](https://crates.io/crates/dydx) `dydx`.\\n:::details[Installation]\\n```bash [Terminal]\\ncargo add dydx\\n```\\n\\nOr add it manually to `Cargo.toml`.\\n\\n```toml [Cargo.toml]\\n[dependencies]\\ndydx = \\\"0.2.0\\\"  # Replace with the latest version // [!code ++]\\n```\\n:::\\n\\n:::note[Configuration File]\\n\\nThe Rust client uses a TOML configuration file to configure several required parameters.\\n\\n:::details[Examples]\\n::::code-group\\n\\n```toml [mainnet.toml]\\n[node]\\nendpoint = \\\"https://dydx-ops-grpc.kingnodes.com:443\\\"\\nchain_id = \\\"dydx-mainnet-1\\\"\\nfee_denom = \\\"ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5\\\"\\n\\n[indexer]\\nhttp.endpoint = \\\"https://indexer.dydx.trade\\\"\\nws.endpoint = \\\"wss://indexer.dydx.trade/v4/ws\\\"\\n\\n[noble] # optional\\nendpoint = \\\"http://noble-grpc.polkachu.com:21590\\\"\\nchain_id = \\\"noble-1\\\"\\nfee_denom = \\\"uusdc\\\"\\n```\\n\\n```toml [testnet.toml]\\n[node]\\nendpoint = \\\"https://test-dydx-grpc.kingnodes.com\\\"\\nchain_id = \\\"dydx-testnet-4\\\"\\nfee_denom = \\\"ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5\\\"\\n\\n[indexer]\\nhttp.endpoint = \\\"https://indexer.v4testnet.dydx.exchange\\\"\\nws.endpoint = \\\"wss://indexer.v4testnet.dydx.exchange/v4/ws\\\"\\n\\n[noble] # optional\\nendpoint = \\\"http://noble-testnet-grpc.polkachu.com:21590\\\"\\nchain_id = \\\"grand-1\\\"\\nfee_denom = \\\"uusdc\\\"\\n\\n[faucet] # optional\\nendpoint = \\\"https://faucet.v4testnet.dydx.exchange\\\"\\n```\\n\\n:::\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/interaction/client/quick-start-rs#quick-start-with-rust\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>This guide will walk you through the steps to set up and start using the dYdX API Rust library.</p>\\n<div data-vocs-steps=\\\"true\\\"><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/client/quick-start-rs.mdx#quick-start-with-rust\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nThis guide will walk you through the steps to set up and start using the dYdX API Rust library.\\n\",\"title\":\"Quick Start with Rust\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/client/quick-start-rs#install-rust-and-cargo\",\"html\":\"<p>Choose and install <a href=\\\"https://www.rust-lang.org/tools/install\\\">Rust</a> and <a href=\\\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/getting-started/installation.html\\\">Cargo</a> for your system.</p></div><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/client/quick-start-rs.mdx#install-rust-and-cargo\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"Choose and install Rust and Cargo for your system.\",\"title\":\"Install Rust and Cargo\",\"titles\":[\"Quick Start with Rust\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/client/quick-start-rs#clone-the-dydx-client-repo\",\"html\":\"<pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">git</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> clone</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients.git</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/client/quick-start-rs.mdx#clone-the-dydx-client-repo\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"git clone https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients.git\",\"title\":\"Clone the dydx client repo\",\"titles\":[\"Quick Start with Rust\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/client/quick-start-rs#run-an-example\",\"html\":\"<p>Go to the Rust client library.</p><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">cd</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> v4-clients/v4-client-rs</span></span></code></pre><p>Now, we can run an example file. Let&#x27;s run <code>accounts_endpoint</code> example.</p><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">cargo</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> run</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> --example</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> account_endpoint</span></span></code></pre></div></div>\\n<strong>Now, you can play around with all the available examples. Happy trading!</strong>\\n<aside data-callout=\\\"tip\\\"><strong data-callout-title=\\\"true\\\">Rust Crate</strong><p>The Rust client is also available through the crates.io <a href=\\\"https://crates.io/crates/dydx\\\">crate</a> <code>dydx</code>.</p><details><summary>Installation</summary><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Terminal\\\" data-lang=\\\"bash\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">cargo</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> add</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\"> dydx</span></span></code></pre><p>Or add it manually to <code>Cargo.toml</code>.</p><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed has-diff\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Cargo.toml\\\" data-lang=\\\"toml\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">dependencies</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line diff add\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">dydx = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;0.2.0&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">  # Replace with the latest version </span></span></code></pre></details></aside>\\n<aside data-callout=\\\"note\\\"><strong data-callout-title=\\\"true\\\">Configuration File</strong><p>The Rust client uses a TOML configuration file to configure several required parameters.</p><details><summary>Examples</summary><div class=\\\"code-group\\\"><div data-title=\\\"mainnet.toml\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"mainnet.toml\\\" data-lang=\\\"toml\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">node</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;https://dydx-ops-grpc.kingnodes.com:443&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">chain_id = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;dydx-mainnet-1&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">fee_denom = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">indexer</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">http.endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;https://indexer.dydx.trade&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">ws.endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;wss://indexer.dydx.trade/v4/ws&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">noble</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">] </span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\"># optional</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;http://noble-grpc.polkachu.com:21590&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">chain_id = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;noble-1&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">fee_denom = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;uusdc&quot;</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"testnet.toml\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"testnet.toml\\\" data-lang=\\\"toml\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">node</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;https://test-dydx-grpc.kingnodes.com&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">chain_id = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;dydx-testnet-4&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">fee_denom = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">indexer</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">http.endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;https://indexer.v4testnet.dydx.exchange&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">ws.endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;wss://indexer.v4testnet.dydx.exchange/v4/ws&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">noble</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">] </span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\"># optional</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;http://noble-testnet-grpc.polkachu.com:21590&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">chain_id = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;grand-1&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">fee_denom = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;uusdc&quot;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">[</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">faucet</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">] </span><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\"># optional</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">endpoint = </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;https://faucet.v4testnet.dydx.exchange&quot;</span></span></code></pre></div></div></details></aside>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/client/quick-start-rs.mdx#run-an-example\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"Go to the Rust client library.cd v4-clients/v4-client-rsNow, we can run an example file. Let&#x27;s run accounts_endpoint example.cargo run --example account_endpoint\\nNow, you can play around with all the available examples. Happy trading!\\nRust CrateThe Rust client is also available through the crates.io crate dydx.Installationcargo add dydxOr add it manually to Cargo.toml.[dependencies]\\ndydx = &quot;0.2.0&quot;  # Replace with the latest version \\nConfiguration FileThe Rust client uses a TOML configuration file to configure several required parameters.Examples[node]\\nendpoint = &quot;https://dydx-ops-grpc.kingnodes.com:443&quot;\\nchain_id = &quot;dydx-mainnet-1&quot;\\nfee_denom = &quot;ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5&quot;\\n \\n[indexer]\\nhttp.endpoint = &quot;https://indexer.dydx.trade&quot;\\nws.endpoint = &quot;wss://indexer.dydx.trade/v4/ws&quot;\\n \\n[noble] # optional\\nendpoint = &quot;http://noble-grpc.polkachu.com:21590&quot;\\nchain_id = &quot;noble-1&quot;\\nfee_denom = &quot;uusdc&quot;[node]\\nendpoint = &quot;https://test-dydx-grpc.kingnodes.com&quot;\\nchain_id = &quot;dydx-testnet-4&quot;\\nfee_denom = &quot;ibc/8E27BA2D5493AF5636760E354E46004562C46AB7EC0CC4C1CA14E9E20E2545B5&quot;\\n \\n[indexer]\\nhttp.endpoint = &quot;https://indexer.v4testnet.dydx.exchange&quot;\\nws.endpoint = &quot;wss://indexer.v4testnet.dydx.exchange/v4/ws&quot;\\n \\n[noble] # optional\\nendpoint = &quot;http://noble-testnet-grpc.polkachu.com:21590&quot;\\nchain_id = &quot;grand-1&quot;\\nfee_denom = &quot;uusdc&quot;\\n \\n[faucet] # optional\\nendpoint = &quot;https://faucet.v4testnet.dydx.exchange&quot;\",\"title\":\"Run an example\",\"titles\":[\"Quick Start with Rust\"]}]}}"
